      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. i want to make it even more impactful for the essay. some critics say that focusing on wealth redistribution ignores individual merit and that people should just work harder to escape poverty. how can i frame that counter-argument as being logically flawed or even morally wrong in my paper?",
