      "content": "that makes sense. for the conclusion of the essay, i want to move away from just \"arguing\" and really drive the point home. how can i phrase the final takeaway so it's clear that the pro-redistribution stance is the only ethically sound position to take, and that anything else is basically just defending an unjust status quo?",
